    {
      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Alright, listen up, foreman! You want the *actual* technical checklist? Fine, but don't think I'm going to give you a boring, dry list. If you don't have a goblin in your head screaming about \"unsecured platforms,\" you're gonna get a goblin in your head screaming about \"missing bolts\" all day long.\n\nHere is the professional, no-nonsense checklist for your crew, but with a side of goblin wisdom to make sure they don't get their heads stuck in the ground:\n\n### **Mandatory Safety Checklist for Scaffolding Setup**\n\n**1. Base Plates & Footing**\n*   **Requirement:** Base plates must be securely bolted to the ground using approved bolts.\n*   **Goblin Check:** If a bolt is missing, the goblin in your head will tell you the scaffolding is \"wobbly.\" You must fix it before anyone steps on it.\n*   **Action:** Verify every single base plate is bolted down. No loose bolts, no wobbly legs.\n\n**2. Planking (Ladder Boards)**\n*   **Requirement:** Planking must be securely fastened to the scaffolding structure.",
